title: Space
content:
Space may refer to:

  • Bank space, the number of spaces remaining in a player's bank
  • Game square, a unit of length
  • Inventory space, the number of spaces a player has left
  • Storage, any interactive content a player utilises to store items, such as accounts (known as mules), banks, bags, pouches, etc.
  • Unknown, inaccessible blank areas on the borders of Gielinor
  • Birdhouse space, location for placing a birdhouse on Fossil Island
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
